## ⚙️ 3. Modulator "Micro-Prompts"
Add these snippets to the **Master Template** to fine-tune specific qualities without rewriting the whole profile.

| Goal | Micro-Prompt Snippet |
|------|----------------------|
| **Make it sound ancient** | `Add "Vocal fry" and slight pitch drift downwards over long vowels.` |
| **Make it sound robotic** | `Set "Quantized articulation"; remove breath noise entirely. Add metallic comb-filtering.` |
| **Make it sound underwater** | `Apply "Low-pass filter at 2kHz"; add "bubble pop" transient artifacts between sentences.` |
| **Make it sound huge** | `Shift pitch down -4 semitones; apply "Sidechain compression" so bass ducks the high end.` |
| **Make it sound ghostly** | `Add "Formant shift up +3 semitones" (chipmunk effect masked by dark reverb); remove consonant transients.` |

